			Point of Interest
			
	*Anghal Desert : first area of this region. Is the second biggest, located in eastern side of it.
		*Golden Coasts : located in the western side of this area, biggest zone here and the place where players grind exp from monsters.
		*Black Sands : located in the eastern side of the area consist in a field of barren desert with many huge blocks of stones and hills.
			*Goldcap Town : this is the first human settlement where the players will arrive once they teleport to this region.Located in the south-west of this area.
			*Choopmine Rigger : this is an ancient mine located in the northestern side of zone. It is a small dungeon inside the mountain.
			*Sundry Lake : a lake which is located right in the center of the area. This lake has the shape of the letter "L", being surrounded by splendid vegetation
		of palm trees and shrubs that make this small place seem like a paradise right in the middle of this desert.